OL,3,CBritishvolt buyer faces assault and
OL,4,Charassment charges in New York
OL,6,FThe man behind the company that is
OL,7,Ftrying to buy Northumberland battery
OL,8,Fstartup Britishvolt has been arrested
OL,9,Fand charged over allegations of
OL,10,Fassault and harassment.
OL,12,FCourt documents filed in New York show
OL,13,Fthat David Collard, 39, faces the
OL,14,Fcharges after an alleged incident on
OL,15,FMadison Avenue on 15 November.
OL,17,FThe allegations mark yet another twist
OL,18,Fin the troubled takeover of
OL,19,FBritishvolt, which went into
OL,20,Fadministration in January 2023.
