OL,6,FMr Collard entered a not guilty plea
OL,7,Fat a court hearing last month and told
OL,8,FITV News in a statement that the
OL,9,Fincident "transpired as a consequence
OL,10,Fof my endeavours to ensure the safety
OL,11,Fof a friend and myself".
OL,13,FWhat are the allegations?
OL,15,FDavid Collard has been charged with
OL,16,Ftwo counts of assault in the third
OL,17,Fdegree, along with three counts of
OL,18,Fharassment.
